Remember that moment you opened the box with those designer shoes you really wanted or that that feeling of driving your first car? It can feel like first love. Can you evoke the same emotion when you get your first smartphone? If that first phone is the Samsung Galaxy A12, you definitely can. When deciding on buying a new device, choosing one that gives you all you need, makes all the difference. For many young South Africans, the Samsung Galaxy A12 is a great first Galaxy – as its packed with heart-skipping premium features offered at an affordable price. That awesome feeling and excitement of unboxing your first-ever smartphone is made extra special with the Galaxy A12. The Galaxy A12 has made cutting-edge innovation accessible to more people – innovation for all. It includes a 5,000mAh all-day battery and an intelligent 48MP Main Camera that empowers you to turn any moment into an exciting photoshoot. It includes the Ultra Wide Camera, so you see and shoot even more of a scene. Additionally, Live Video is a big part of young people’s lives so the incredible quad rear camera is a welcome feature, which makes it possible to do more of what you love, in a way that expresses who you are. The Galaxy A12 also includes an 8MP front camera which incorporates Live Focus as well as Smart Beauty to ensure that your selfies are always on point. For young people who choose a Galaxy device as their first device or next one, the Galaxy A12 does not disappoint. It’s impressive 6.5” display is an HD+ Infinity-V display, ensures a fully immersive experience. So whether you’re watching videos or gaming you’ll enjoy every moment. Also, its innovation and seamless integration into the Samsung ecosystem of products and services makes it an all-around good choice for those who want to do more. Impressively, with all these premium features, you can now buy the Galaxy A12, for a recommended retail price of only R3499 at any participating retailer, Samsung online store, or any Samsung brand store. Those who purchase this amazing device will receive a R200 cashback voucher with their purchase. Its incredible value will definitely appeal to those who want a smartphone worth falling in love with. To ensure you can protect your device the offer includes the option to add Samsung Care+ that offers screen damage protection for only R99 once-off, valued at R4993. Additionally, should you have an older device you can trade it in for an applicable device and get up to R1800 off the purchase price4. What’s not to love! For more information on the Galaxy A12 click here. <img class="aligncenter wp-image-386082 size-large" src="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Samsung-A12-png1-1-640x430.png" alt="" width="640" height="430" srcset="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Samsung-A12-png1-1.png 640w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Samsung-A12-png1-1-595x400.png 595w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Samsung-A12-png1-1-300x202.png 300w" sizes="(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: 909px) 67vw, (max-width: 984px) 61vw, (max-width: 1362px) 45vw, 600px" /> <img class="aligncenter wp-image-386084 size-large" src="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Samsung-A12-png2-1-640x430.png" alt="" width="640" height="430" srcset="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Samsung-A12-png2-1.png 640w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Samsung-A12-png2-1-595x400.png 595w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Samsung-A12-png2-1-300x202.png 300w" sizes="(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: 909px) 67vw, (max-width: 984px) 61vw, (max-width: 1362px) 45vw, 600px" /> <img class="aligncenter wp-image-386086 size-large" src="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Samsung-A12-png3-1-640x430.png" alt="" width="640" height="430" srcset="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Samsung